data.description: Welcome home to your stunning 2 story, 3 bedrooms, loft 2 1/2 bath with a 2 car garage 1777 soft home located in Silverado Ranch community. Kitchen has lots of counter space with an island, and cabinets for storage, countertops are granite with tile back splash. Beautiful flooring, window covering throughout the home.  Upstairs 3 bedrooms and a LARGE LOFT, washer and dry located upstairs so no hauling laundry up and down stairs.  Which are included along with the refrigerator Ceiling fans in all bedrooms, Easy access to freeways, close to strip and airport.  Very clean and move in ready.   See today don’t miss out on this home!!!
